author: knoxnews.com
title: Soccer: Webb blanks Franklin Road Academy - PrepXtra
text:
Reeves' goal gives Webb 1-0 region win over FRA
Lexi Reeves scored with an assist from Darby Bauman in the second half to give Webb School a 1-0 soccer victory over Franklin Road Academy on Saturday in a East/Middle Region semifinal match.
Webb (15-1-2) will play Battle Ground Academy on Tuesday at 5 p.m. Eastern at University School of Nashville.
The victory over FRA ensured the Spartans will host a sectional game for the first time on Saturday.
Webb out-shot Franklin Road Academy 10-6.
New Sentinel staff
